### ================================

### 🔐 AUTH APIs

### ================================

### Register User

POST http://localhost:5248/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
"name": "Vijay",
"email": "[vijay@gmail.com](mailto:vijay@gmail.com)",
"password": "123456"
}

### Login User

POST http://localhost:5248/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "[vijay@gmail.com](mailto:vijay@gmail.com)",
"password": "123456"
}

