### ================================

### ⚖️ QUANTITY APIs (PROTECTED)

### ================================

### Compare

POST http://localhost:5248/api/quantity/compare
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

[
{ "value": 10, "unit": "Feet" },
{ "value": 120, "unit": "Inch" }
]

### Convert

POST http://localhost:5248/api/quantity/convert/Meter
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
"value": 10,
"unit": "Feet"
}

### Addition

POST http://localhost:5248/api/quantity/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

[
{ "value": 5, "unit": "Feet" },
{ "value": 5, "unit": "Feet" }
]

### Subtraction

POST http://localhost:5248/api/quantity/subtract
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

[
{ "value": 10, "unit": "Feet" },
{ "value": 5, "unit": "Feet" }
]

### Division

POST http://localhost:5248/api/quantity/divide
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

[
{ "value": 10, "unit": "Feet" },
{ "value": 5, "unit": "Feet" }
]
